@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 01. A2A Supervisor Agent System Context (Python runtime)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor User

rectangle "Client Channel" {
  [Web UI / API Client] as Client
}

rectangle "Supervisor Agent (smart-supervisor)" {
  [supervisor_a2a_endpoint] as supervisor_a2a_endpoint
  [supervisor_a2a_request_validator] as supervisor_a2a_request_validator
  [SupervisorAgentService] as supervisor_agent_service
  [ExecutionConsistencyCoordinator\n(Idempotency & Atomic State)] as execution_consistency_coordinator
  [HitlGateService] as hitl_gate_service
  [SupervisorExecutionPersistenceService] as supervisor_execution_persistence_service #F3F4F6
  [SupervisorPersistenceStrategyFactory] as supervisor_persistence_strategy_factory
  [SupervisorGraphExecutionService] as supervisor_graph_execution_service #F3F4F6
  [LangGraph CompiledGraph] as langgraph_compiled_graph #DCEBFF
  [PlanningService\n(LLM Planning)] as planning_service
  [DefaultA2AInvocationService] as a2a_invocation_service
  [HandoffPolicyService] as handoff_policy_service
  [SupervisorResponseComposeService] as supervisor_response_compose_service #FDE7C7
  [PreHitlA2uiService] as pre_hitl_a2ui_service
  [DefaultSupervisorLlmRuntime] as default_supervisor_llm_runtime
  [SupervisorExceptionTranslator] as supervisor_exception_translator
}

database "Stores / Redis or InMemory" as Stores {
  [Conversation Store] as ConversationStore #D9F7E8
  [Graph Checkpoint Store] as CheckpointStore #FFD9E2
  [Swarm State Store] as SwarmStateStore #E7D9FF
  [Review Store] as ReviewStore
  [Task Store] as TaskStore
  [Execution Snapshot Store] as ExecutionSnapshotStore
}

cloud "Downstream A2A Agents" {
  [Domain Agent A2A 1] as ProductAgent
  [Domain Agent A2A 2] as ReservationAgent
}

artifact "settings/app.yml / settings/supervisor.yml / settings/supervisor-hitl.yml" as Config

User --> Client
Client --> supervisor_a2a_endpoint : /a2a/supervisor\nJSON-RPC + SSE
supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> supervisor_a2a_request_validator
supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> supervisor_agent_service
supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> supervisor_exception_translator
supervisor_agent_service --> execution_consistency_coordinator : reserve_request
supervisor_agent_service --> hitl_gate_service
supervisor_agent_service --> supervisor_execution_persistence_service
supervisor_agent_service --> supervisor_graph_execution_service
hitl_gate_service --> supervisor_execution_persistence_service
hitl_gate_service --> planning_service
supervisor_execution_persistence_service --> supervisor_persistence_strategy_factory
supervisor_persistence_strategy_factory --> execution_consistency_coordinator
supervisor_graph_execution_service -[#4C8BF5]-> langgraph_compiled_graph
langgraph_compiled_graph --> a2a_invocation_service
langgraph_compiled_graph --> handoff_policy_service
supervisor_graph_execution_service -[#E3A23B]-> supervisor_response_compose_service
supervisor_response_compose_service --> pre_hitl_a2ui_service
planning_service --> default_supervisor_llm_runtime
supervisor_response_compose_service --> default_supervisor_llm_runtime
a2a_invocation_service --> Config
a2a_invocation_service --> ProductAgent
a2a_invocation_service --> ReservationAgent
supervisor_graph_execution_service --> supervisor_execution_persistence_service
execution_consistency_coordinator --> TaskStore
execution_consistency_coordinator --> ReviewStore
execution_consistency_coordinator --> CheckpointStore
execution_consistency_coordinator --> SwarmStateStore
execution_consistency_coordinator --> ExecutionSnapshotStore

note right of supervisor_agent_service
Current request entry flow
- validate + sanitize input
- planner-backed `review_required` evaluation
- planner review parse/runtime failure defaults to review-required or reject
- create immutable reviewed execution snapshot before WAITING_REVIEW
- execute orchestrator only when review is not required
- all Redis writes enter via persistence facade
end note

note right of supervisor_graph_execution_service
Current execution flow
- load immutable execution snapshot + history/checkpoint/swarm
- run LangGraph
- invoke downstream A2A agents
- evaluate/apply handoff
- compose text or A2UI response
- emit typed output events
- persist only final result channels to task state
end note
@enduml
